description:
&lt;p&gt;gtd healthcare are currently recruiting clinical assessors to join the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The clinical assessor will function as part of a health care team providing a comprehensive clinical assessment service to patients and/or their carers/relatives resulting in a safe and appropriate clinical decision.and experience in frailty paediatrics and mental health.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To facilitate the provision of accurate healthcare information, health improvement advice or, where applicable, referral to the appropriate level and location of care, in order to meet the holistic and therapeutic requirements of the patient/carer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information on the role please contact Audrey Leech, Clinical Lead on audrey.leech@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
